<paragraph blockId="13.[189,1398,614,680]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">
From the Greek, 
<emphasis box="[395,485,614,639]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">syssitos</emphasis>
a messmate and 
<emphasis box="[693,742,614,639]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">mya</emphasis>
a clam, referring to the commensal habit and bacterial symbiosis.
</paragraph>
